$grp PS_MissionDescription : "{3136BE42592F3B1B}PrefabsEditable/MissionDescription/EditableMissionDescription.et" {
 SIT {
  coords 4176.552 0 11809.229
  m_sTitle "Situation"
  m_sTextData "<h2>PRELIMS</h2> "\
  "Date: 1st May 2020"\
  "Time: Random"\
  "Location: Mull of Kintyre, Scotland"\
  "Weather: Random"\
  ""\
  "<h2>LORE</h2> "\
  "Radical environmentalists from the Earth Contamination Outfit (ECO) have launched a surprise attack on a TEM POWER oil rig off the coast of Scotland."\
  ""\
  "British intelligence has been monitoring the group for several years as their activities and influence have grown within the UK. Despite this surveillance, the planning and preparation for this operation — including the movement of weapons and equipment — managed to evade detection."\
  ""\
  "The ECO has carried out smaller-scale actions across the country before, but nothing approaching the scale of this attack."\
  "Earlier today, the militants arrived by boat and boarded the platform via the access stairs, quickly overpowering rig personnel and seizing control of the installation. A number of crew members were able to escape using lifeboats, but several were captured during the takeover."\
  "Current reports indicate that five workers are being held hostage somewhere on the platform."\
  ""\
  "Royal Marines have been tasked with conducting an assault on the rig, eliminating the hostile elements, and securing the hostages. The situation is volatile, and the militants may attempt to use the hostages as leverage once contact is made."\
  ""\
  "Time is critical. The rig must be retaken and the remaining crew recovered."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 EN {
  coords 4175.058 0 11803.487
  m_sTitle "Enemy forces"
  m_sTextData "<h2>COMPOSITION & DISPOSITION</h2>"\
  "Enemy forces are the Earth Contamination Outfit. "\
  "A known terrorist group that have been conducting attacks through the UK."\
  "Reports from the crew members who managed to flee say the enemy troops number around 10x people."\
  ""\
  "They're located at the TEM POWER oil rig at GRID: 048017"\
  ""\
  "<h2>STRENGTHS & CAPABILITIES</h2>"\
  "Crew members said they saw various wepons, machine gun both small and big, rifles, shotguns, some that looked modern, some that looked old."\
  "The enemy outfit wore a camo red patterned unifom with yet again various hats, helmets, vests, and backpacks of different colours and patterns."\
  ""\
  "Observations show no armed vessels."\
  "We don't know what equipment they have. Be cautious of booby traps and alike."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 FRN {
  coords 4171.156 0 11794.047
  m_sTitle "Friendly forces"
  m_sTextData "<h2>COMPOSITION & DISPOSITION</h2>"\
  "We are the British 42 Commando raiding troop."\
  "Total strength is 31 personnel, including pilots and aircrew, giving us 28 ground troops."\
  "Our current location is the airfield at GRID: 048117."\
  ""\
  "<h2>STRENGTHS & CAPABILITIES</h2>"\
  "We have several methods of insertion onto the rig:"\
  ""\
  "• A: Utilize the helicopters at our current location to fly directly to the rig and land on the platform."\
  "• B: Teleport via the flagpole to one of three docks located at GRID 058035, GRID 027018, and GRID 077006."\
  "Each dock has RHIB fast raiding boats which can be used to approach the access stairs located on the legs of the rig."\
  "• C: Deploy via steerable parachutes. Interact with the flagpole to teleport to a platform 1500m above the rig. Parachutes are available at the platform."\
  "• D: A combination of any of the above methods."\
  ""\
  "Sappers are equipped with small demolition charges and wire cutters should the situation require their use."\
  ""\
  "<h2>SERVICE AND SUPPORT</h2>"\
  "• Two GPMG-armed UH-1H helicopters are available at the staging location."\
  "There are 16 spare troop seats available in total, with aircrew already accounted for."\
  "• Each dock contains 3x .50cal RHIBs, each capable of carrying 9 personnel."\
  "Note that the elevation on the mounted guns may not be sufficient to engage targets on the upper levels of the rig once in close proximity."\
  "• A supply crate at spawn contains extendable ladders and handheld periscopes."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
 CS {
  coords 4166.849 0 11779.042
  m_sTitle "Comsig"
  m_sTextData "<h2>CALLSIGNS</h2>"\
  "• <b>TRP HQ</b> - 11"\
  "• <b>TRP OC</b> - 11A"\
  "• <b>TRP SGT</b> - 11B"\
  "• <b>1SEC</b> - 11C"\
  "• <b>2SEC</b> - 11D"\
  "• <b>3SEC</b>- 11E"\
  "• <b>4SEC</b> - 11F"\
  ""\
  "<h2>RADIO FREQS</h2>"\
  "• <b>Troop net</b> - 40hz | <b>Air net</b> - 40.5hz "\
  "• <b>HQ</b> - 39.5hz"\
  "• <b>1st SEC</b> - 39hz"\
  "• <b>2nd SEC</b> - 38.5hz"\
  "• <b>3rd SEC</b> - 38hz"\
  "• <b>4th SEC</b> - 37.5hz"\
  ""\
  "<h2>MISC</h2>"\
  " <b>Challenge:</b> Silver | <b>Password:</b> Birch"\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 5
 }
 MIS {
  coords 4175.525 0 11803.824
  m_sTitle "Mission"
  m_sTextData "<h2>MISSION STATEMENT</h2>"\
  "Our mission is to conduct a DELIBERATE RAID on the TEM POWER oil rig in order to DESTROY the hostile forces onboard, SECURE any hostages, and DEFUSE the bomb which ECO militants claim will detonate in approximately 35 minutes."\
  ""\
  "<h2>OBJECTIVES</h2>"\
  "This is a complex and confined environment. Careful selection of entry points, coordinated timing, and clear communication will be critical to mission success."\
  ""\
  "<b>PRIMARY:</b> Defuse the bomb planted on the rig."\
  "Crew members who escaped reported seeing a large bomb looking device being carried into the central compound on the ground floor, located at the base of the main tower."\
  "CCTV has confirmed the presence of this object, matching witness descriptions."\
  ""\
  "Our sappers assess that if we can secure and hold the compound for several minutes — approximately five — they will have a strong chance of successfully defusing the device."\
  ""\
  "<b>SECONDARY:</b> Neutralize the hostile ECO presence on the rig by any necessary means."\
  ""\
  "<b>OPTIONAL:</b> Recover the 5 missing crew members believed to be held hostage somewhere on the platform."\
  "While their safety is important, the priority remains preventing the destruction of the rig and the wider threat this poses."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
}